Package com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.price

Contains replacement command extension and response extension classes for the Domain Name Price Extension.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DomainCheckPriceResponseExtension
    Representation of the EPP Domain Check response extension for Pricing Check aspect of the Domain Name Check Pricing extension.
    DomainCheckPricingCommandExtension
    Extension for the EPP Domain Check command, representing the Pricing Check aspect of the Domain Name Pricing extension.
    DomainCreatePriceCommandExtension
    Extension for the EPP Domain Create command, representing the Create Premium Domain aspect of the Domain Name Price Extension.
    DomainRenewPriceCommandExtension
    Extension for the EPP Domain Renew command, representing the Renew Premium Domain aspect of the Domain Name Price extension.
    DomainTransferRequestPriceCommandExtension
    Extension for the EPP Domain Transfer command, representing the Transfer Premium Domain aspect of the Domain Name Price extension.
    PriceInfo
    Contains the price information of a domain returned in a check response extension.
